<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/armed-forces-covenant-fund-trust> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Armed Forces Covenant Fund Trust started work in May 2015 with £10-million per annum funding from the MOD using Libor funds. It will have distributed £50-million by the end of March 2020 supporting a range of programmes for veterans, their carers and families, serving families and supporting integration of the military and civilian communities. Armed Forces Covenant Fund Trust is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Defence ."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
